'''Stuart''' is an intern at [[Seattle Presbyterian Hospital]].

==History==
When Bailey came into Seattle Pres believing she was having a heart attack, Stuart was sent to do a workup and run tests on her. He told her she wasn't having a heart attack, but she insisted that she was and eventually, Stuart was replaced by [[Chief of Surgery]], [[Larry Maxwell]].

==Career==
He is a surgical intern at [[Seattle Presbyterian Hospital]].
